name: 凯拉·迪薇内瑞
name_full: 凯拉·迪薇内瑞 Kayla DiVenere
introduction: Kayla began acting at age 6, when her first big audition was for Renesmee in the Twilight series "Breaking Dawn". After that her name went viral on the Internet in support for her. She went on to book several commercials and modelling work as well as a TV movie and a short film. Kayla's passion for acting shows through as she is natural and portrays a great range of emotions. Kayla has maturity way beyond her years. When she is not busy acting she loves to sing, dance, play piano, and skip rope with her friends. Her brother Daniel is an actor as well.
